Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.77,0:01:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,(本片開始)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,係長你這樣我很困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,又有女員工投訴你性騷擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.76,0:04:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是不小心碰到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,她說你手都貼上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你是像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣摸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.79,0:04:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,還是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,係長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你老是做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,難怪升不上去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼喜歡年輕的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你臉好下流
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你在抖什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你坐上來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.85,0:08:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,舌頭伸出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,變好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,可以脫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這什麼鮪魚肚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.74,0:13:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你抖什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,想被我舔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,係長的肉棒好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.78,0:14:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,能用力點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我想看你射
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,還射不夠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,幫你尻乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,射出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,射出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,射乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,射好多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我會跟社長報告的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,弟弟早
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,有睡飽飽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,要吃飯飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,有睡好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.76,0:17:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,內褲濕濕的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,又尿床了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:17:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,幫你弄乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.74,0:18:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,濕嗒嗒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.75,0:18:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,內褲都濕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.82,0:18:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,脫掉玀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:18:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,大腿也濕了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,擦乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.86,0:19:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,變大了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,鳥鳥好有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.75,0:19:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我最喜弟的鳥鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,幫你尻尻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,會抖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,越來越硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,要用老師的手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.82,0:21:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.79,0:21:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.86,0:21:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己尻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.87,0:21:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,手給我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣尻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.82,0:22:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服嗎
