Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.75,0:23:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,想看老師自慰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.80,0:23:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,看得到內褲嗎
